_sText:
OK, this is a re release of socutzknivez 2005, this is the better version (had to have jugrknot fix some stuff for me) and the lighting outside was fixed so there is no longer an enormous black area on one of the sides, skybox was re scaled, and water in the middle was added. 

You get your scout (of course) a p228 (HIGHLY underrated pistol) and your knife. 

Captain[T]rippy 

And thx to jugrknot for helping fix it.

Same screens as before (plus 2), but map is better.

I have included the vmf for any mappers wanting to modify it and they Have my permission to do so as long as credit is given for original.
